N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-1.14 - Personal injury or property damage

State Regulations

If an employee or visitor is injured or their vehicle
is damaged in a State operated parking area, the individual must report the
details of the incident on forms available at any parking attendant station, as
soon as possible. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9

296-1.14
